sin,cos = math.sin,math.cos pi = 3.141592
-- Drawing function
function sdA(x,y,r,th1,th2,R,G,B) ssC(R,G,B) for i=th1,th2-1,1 do sdL(x+r*cos(pi/12*i),y+r*sin(pi/12*i),x+r*cos(pi/12*(i+1)),y+r*sin(pi/12*(i+1))) end end
function sdAF(x,y,r,th1,th2,R,G,B) ssC(R,G,B) for j=1,r,0.5 do for i=th1,th2-1,1 do sdL(x+j*cos(pi/12*i),y+j*sin(pi/12*i),x+j*cos(pi/12*(i+1)),y+j*sin(pi/12*(i+1))) end end end
function sdS(x,y,r,th1,th2,scale,R,G,B) ssC(R,G,B) th,r1,r2,r3 = pi/12,r-1,r-2,r-3 for i=th1,th2,2 do sdL(x+r*cos(th*i),y+r*sin(th*i),x+r3*cos(th*i),y+r3*sin(th*i)) end ssC(R,G,B,150) if scale>1 then for i=th1,th2-1,2/scale do sdL(x+r1*cos(th*i),y+r1*sin(th*i),x+r2*cos(th*i),y+r2*sin(th*i)) end end end
-- Drawing Markings
function drawTemp(x,y) sdL(x+1,y+1,x+3,y+1) sdL(x+1,y,x+1,y+5) sdL(x,y+3,x+3,y+3) end
function drawFuel(x,y) sdR(x,y,2,3) sdRF(x,y+2,3,3) end
function drawBat(x,y) sdR(x,y+1,4,2) sdL(x+1,y,x+1,y+1) sdL(x+3,y,x+3,y+1) end
function drawTempR(x,y) sdL(x,y,x,y+5) sdL(x,y,x+2,y) sdL(x,y+2,x+2,y+2) sdL(x-3,y+4,x-1,y+4) sdL(x+3,y+4,x+1,y+4) sdL(x-2,y+6,x+3,y+6) end
function drawFuelR(x,y) sdR(x+1,y,3,3) sdRF(x+1,y+3,4,3) sdL(x,y+6,x+6,y+6) sdL(x+5,y+1,x+7,y+2) sdL(x+5,y+4,x+7,y+2) end
function drawBatR(x,y) sdR(x,y+3,6,3) sdL(x+1,y+2,x+3,y+3) sdL(x+5,y+2,x+5,y+3) end
function drawBrake(x,y) sdR(x,y,2,2) sdR(x+4,y,2,2) sdRF(x,y+4,7,3) end
function drawReverse(x,y) sdL(x-1,y+1,x-1,y+6) sdL(x+1,y+1,x+1,y+6) for i=1,3 do sdL(x-3,y+2*i-1,x-2,y+2*i-1) sdL(x+3,y+2*i-1,x+2,y+2*i-1) end end
function drawDoor(x,y) sdR(x-2,y,3,6) sdL(x-2,y+1,x+2,y+1) sdL(x-2,y+5,x+2,y+5) sdL(x-3,y+2,x-5,y+4) sdL(x+2,y+2,x+4,y+4) end
-- Main Function
function onTick() SPD,SPM,ENT,ENR,FLC,FLL,BAT,SPU,RSM = igN(1),igN(2),igN(3),igN(4),igN(5),igN(6),igN(7),igN(8),igN(9) DOR,INR,INL,BRK,REV = igB(1),igB(2),igB(3),igB(4),igB(5) if ENT>100 or BRK == true or BAT<0.1 or DOR == true then EME = true else EME = false end end
function onDraw() w,h,wh,hh,wq,hq=96,32,48,16,24,8 ssC(5,5,5) screen.drawClear()
ssC(255,255,255) drawTemp(17,h-6) drawFuel(13,hh-1) drawBat(w-20,h-5)
--RPS
ssC(10,10,10) sdL(wh-16,hh,wh-1,hh) sdAF(wh-16,hh,hh-1,9,24.7,10,10,10) sdA(wh-16,hh,hh-1,9,24.7,255,255,255) sdL(wh-1,hh-1,wh-1,hh+1) sdA(wh-16,hh,hh-3,20,24.7,200,0,0) sdA(wh-16,hh,hh-4,20,24.7,200,0,0) sdS(wh-16,hh,hh-1,9,24.7,2,255,255,255)
--Speed sdAF(wh+16,hh,hh-1,12,27,10,10,10) sdA(wh+16,hh,hh-1,12,27,255,255,255) sdS(wh+16,hh,hh-1,12,27,2,255,255,255)
--Temp sdA(9,h-3,8,14,22,255,255,255) sdA(9,h-3,7,20,22,200,0,0) sdS(9,h-3,8,14,22,0,255,255,255)
--Fuel sdA(8,hh,8,14,22,255,255,255) sdA(8,hh,7,14,16,200,0,0) sdS(8,hh,8,14,22,0,255,255,255)
--Battery sdA(w-9,h-3,8,14,22,255,255,255) sdA(w-9,h-3,7,14,16,200,0,0) sdS(w-9,h-3,8,14,22,0,255,255,255)
ssC(7,7,7) sdCF(wh-16,hh,3) sdCF(wh+16,hh,3) sdCF(9,h-3,2) sdCF(8,hh,2) sdCF(w-9,h-3,2)
ssC(255,0,0) if EME == true then sdL(wh,1,wh-3,6) sdL(wh,1,wh+3,6) sdL(wh-2,6,wh+3,6) end if ENT > 100 then drawTempR(w-13,4) end if BRK == true then drawBrake(wh+16,h-8) end if BAT<0.25 then drawBatR(w-12,11) end if DOR == true then drawDoor(wh-19,h-8) end
ssC(165,70,10) if FLL/FLC < 0.25 then drawFuelR(w-8,4) end
ssC(20,230,20)
if INL == true then sdRF(wh+28,2,4,3) sdL(wh+30,3,wh+33,3) sdL(wh+30,1,wh+30,6) end if INR == true then sdRF(wh-31,2,4,3) sdL(wh-30,3,wh-33,3) sdL(wh-30,1,wh-30,6) end if REV == true then drawReverse(6,0) end
end

--Small number
function zero(x,y) sdR(x,y,2,4) end function one(x,y) sdL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function two(x,y) sdL(x,y,x+3,y) sdL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) sdL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) sdL(x+2,y,x+2,y+2) sdL(x,y+2,x,y+4) end function three(x,y) sdL(x,y,x+3,y) sdL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) sdL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) sdL(x+2,y,x+2,y+4) end function four(x,y) sdL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) sdL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) sdL(x,y,x,y+2) end function five(x,y) sdL(x,y,x+3,y) sdL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) sdL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) sdL(x,y,x,y+2) sdL(x+2,y+2,x+2,y+4) end function six(x,y) sdR(x,y+2,2,2) sdL(x,y,x+3,y) sdL(x,y,x,y+2) end function seven(x,y) sdL(x,y,x+3,y) sdL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function eight(x,y) sdR(x,y,2,4) sdL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) end function nine(x,y) sdR(x,y,2,2) sdL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) sdL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) end
function CSN(x,y,n) if n=="0" then zero(x,y) elseif n=="1" then one(x,y) elseif n=="2" then two(x,y) elseif n=="3" then three(x,y) elseif n=="4" then four(x,y) elseif n=="5" then five(x,y) elseif n=="6" then six(x,y) elseif n=="7" then seven(x,y) elseif n=="8" then eight(x,y) elseif n=="9" then nine(x,y) end end
function dsN(x,y,s) s=tostring(s) l=string.len(s) for i=1,l do n=s:sub(i,i) CSN(x,y,n) x=x+4 end
end
-- Main Function
Dist = 0
function onTick() SPD,SPM,ENT,ENR,FLC,FLL,BAT,SPU,RMM = igN(1),igN(2),igN(3),igN(4),igN(5),igN(6),igN(7),igN(8),igN(9) DOR,INR,INL = igB(1),igB(2),igB(3) if SPU == 1 then SPD = SPD*3.6 elseif SPU == 2 then SPD = SPD*2.236936 end if RMM == 2 then ENR = ENR*60 end Dist = Dist + SPD/216000 Distk = math.floor(Dist) Distm = math.floor((Dist-math.floor(Dist))*10)
P_SPD = SPD/SPM P_ENT = ENT/150 P_ENR = ENR/RMM P_FLL = FLL/FLC P_BAT = BAT
if P_SPD > 1 then P_SPD = 1 - math.random()*0.05 end if P_ENT > 1 then P_ENT = 1 - math.random()*0.05 end if P_ENR > 1 then P_ENR = 1 - math.random()*0.05 end
end
function onDraw() w,h,wh,hh,wq,hq=96,32,48,16,24,8
ssC(50,60,35) sdRF(wh-13,hh+4,27,9) sdRF(wh+10,hh-10,13,7) sdRF(wh-20,hh-10,9,7) ssC(30,40,15) sdL(wh-20,hh-10,wh-11,hh-10) sdL(wh-20,hh-10,wh-20,hh-3) sdL(wh+10,hh-10,wh+23,hh-10) sdL(wh+10,hh-10,wh+10,hh-3) sdL(wh-13,hh+4,wh+14,hh+4) sdL(wh-13,hh+4,wh-13,hh+13) ssC(40,50,25) dsN(wh-11,hh+6,stf("%4.1f", 8888.8)) dsN(wh+11,hh-9,stf("%3.0f", 888)) dsN(wh-19,hh-9,stf("%2.0f", 88)) ssC(3,3,3) sdL(wh+6, hh+10,wh+7,hh+10) dsN(wh-11,hh+6,stf("%4.0f", Distk)) dsN(wh+9,hh+6,stf("%1.0f", Distm)) dsN(wh+11,hh-9,stf("%3.0f", SPD)) dsN(wh-19,hh-9,stf("%2.0f", ENR))
ssC(255,0,0) --RPS sdL(wh-16+(hh-3)*cos(pis*(9+15*P_ENR)),hh+(hh-3)*sin(pis*(9+15*P_ENR)),wh-16,hh) --Speed sdL(wh+16+(hh-3)*cos(pis*(12+15*P_SPD)),hh+(hh-3)*sin(pis*(12+15*P_SPD)),wh+16,hh) --Temp sdL(9+6*cos(pis*(14+8*P_ENT)),h-3+6*sin(pis*(14+8*P_ENT)),9,h-3) --Fuel sdL(8+6*cos(pis*(14+8*P_FLL)),hh+6*sin(pis*(14+8*P_FLL)),8,hh) --Battery sdL(w-9+6*cos(pis*(14+8*P_BAT)),h-3+6*sin(pis*(14+8*P_BAT)),w-9,h-3)
end
